---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Projects" description="A list of my programming projects across Python, web frameworks, and more.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Projects</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>Python</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Number database — <a href="https://www.datanab.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">datanab.net</a></li>
      <li>Vigenère cipher — <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/Python/tree/master/cipher" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      <li>Hex board that draws a line between two selected hexes — <a href="/python-hex">details</a></li>
      <li>Budget planner built with PyQt — <a href="/pynance">details</a></li>
      <li>Python library for the Robinhood Financial API — <a href="https://pypi.org/project/robin-stocks/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a> · <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/robin_stocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>Flask</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Hello world with AngularJS frontend — <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/flask/tree/master/project1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>Django</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Online list with a unique URL per visitor</li>
      <li>Poll app from the Django tutorial</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>AngularJS</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Web version of the Python hex board</li>
      <li>Todo list with local storage</li>
      <li>JSON data loader from a web server</li>
      <li>Searchable list with multiple views using the <code>$route</code> service</li>
      <li>Home portal with stopwatch and currency converter (multiple controllers)</li>
      <li>Form examples: checkboxes, ngModelOptions, ngMessages, styling</li>
      <li>ngSwitch with controllers — list created and destroyed on each click</li>
      <li>ngSwitch with services — list stored at global scope and never destroyed</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>React</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Android-style calculator — <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/Android/tree/master/Project1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>Bash</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Script to auto-generate new programming files with a header — <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/Bash/blob/master/make_file.sh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>LabVIEW</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reads names from a CSV and organizes them into groups — <a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/Labview/tree/master/GroupSorter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
